# Privacy Policy

**Effective Date:** [May 08, 2025]

This Privacy Policy explains how Snowflake Insights ("we", "us") handles your information.

## 1. Data Collection
We may collect user IDs, server IDs, and channel IDs for basic bot functionality. We do **not** collect personal information.

## 2. Data Usage
Collected data is used solely to enable bot features such as command responses and server-specific configurations.

## 3. Data Sharing
We do not share, sell, or distribute any collected data to third parties.

## 4. Data Storage
All data is securely stored and only accessible by the bot owner. Data is removed upon bot removal or user request.

